\c 19
\s Kunatswa kwevasina kuchena
\p
\v 1 Zvino Jehovha wakataura kuna Mozisi nekuna Aroni achiti:
\v 2 Ichi chimiso chemurairo Jehovha waakaraira achiti: Taura kuvana vaIsraeri kuti vakuvigire tsiru dzvuku risina gwapa, risina chipomerwa pariri, pasina kumboiswa joko pariri\x + Det. 21.3. 1 Zvak. 6.7.\x*.
\v 3 Zvino mucharipa kuna Eriazari mupristi, kuti aribudisire kunze kwemusasa, ndokuriuraya pamberi pechiso chake\x + Rev. 4.12. VaHeb. 13.11.\x*.
\v 4 Zvino Eriazari mupristi achatora paropa raro nemunwe wake, ndokusasa zveropa raro pakatarisa mberi kwetende rekusangana kanomwe\x + Rev. 4.6,17; 16.14,19. VaHeb. 9.13.\x*.
\v 5 Zvino kuchapiswa tsiru pamberi pemeso ake; kuchapiswa dehwe raro nenyama yaro neropa raro pamwe nemazvizvi aro\x + Eki. 29.14. Rev. 4.11,12.\x*.
\v 6 Zvino mupristi achatora rutanda rwemusidhari, nehisopi, nezvitsvuku, ndokukandira pakati pekupiswa kwetsiru\x + Rev. 14.4,6,49.\x*.
\v 7 Zvino mupristi achasuka nguvo dzake, uye achashambidza muviri wake mumvura, uye pashure achapinda mumusasa; mupristi agova asina kuchena kusvika madekwani\x + 19.8,10. Rev. 11.25; 15.5.\x*.
\v 8 Neanoripisa achasuka nguvo dzake mumvura, nekushambidza muviri wake mumvura, agova asina kuchena kusvika madekwani\x + 19.5.\x*.
\v 9 Zvino murume wakachena achaunganidza madota etsiru, ndokuaisa kunze kwemusasa\x + VaHeb. 9.13.\x* panzvimbo yakachena\x + Rev. 4.12; 6.11; 10.14.\x*, kuti achengeterwe ungano yevana vaIsraeri, ive mvura yekuparadzanisa; kunatswa kwechivi\x + 19.13,20,21. Num. 31.23.\x*.
\v 10 Zvino anounganidza madota etsiru achasuka nguvo dzake, agova asina kuchena kusvika madekwani; chichava chimiso nekusingaperi kuvana vaIsraeri nekumweni agere semutorwa pakati pavo.
\p
\v 11 Anogunzva wakafa, chitunha chemunhu upi neupi achava asina kuchena mazuva manomwe\x + 19.16. Rev. 21.1. Num. 5.2; 9.6,10. 19.22. Hag. 2.13.\x*.
\v 12 Iye achazvichenura nayo nezuva retatu, uye nezuva rechinomwe achava akachena; asi kana asingazvichenuri nezuva retatu, haangavi akachena nezuva rechinomwe\x + 31.19.\x*.
\v 13 Ani nani anogunzva wakafa, chitunha chemunhu wakafa, akasazvichenura, anosvibisa tabhenakeri yaJehovha\x + 19.20. Rev. 15.31.\x*; uye mweya uyu uchagurwa kubva paIsraeri; nokuti mvura yekuparadzanisa haina kusaswa paari, achava asina kuchena\x + Rev. 7.20.\x*; kusachena kwake kuchiri pamusoro pake\x + Rev. 7.20.\x*.
\v 14 Uyu murairo panofa munhu mutende: Umwe neumwe anopinda mutende neumwe neumwe ari mutende achava asina kuchena mazuva manomwe.
\v 15 Nemudziyo umwe neumwe wakashama usina chifunhiro chakasungirwa pauri uchava usina kuchena\x + Rev. 11.32. Num. 31.20.\x*.
\v 16 Uye ani nani anogunzva wakaurawa mubani nemunondo, kana wakafa, kana pfupa remunhu, kana bwiro, achava asina kuchena mazuva manomwe\x + 19.11.\x*.
\v 17 Zvino vachatorera usina kuchena pamadota ekupiswa kwekuchenurwa kwechivi, mvura inoyerera igoiswa pamusoro pawo mumudziyo\x + 19.6,9.\x*.
\v 18 Zvino murume wakachena achatora hisopi ndokuinyika mumvura, ndokuisasa patende nepamidziyo yose nepavanhu vaivapo nepane akagunzva pfupa kana wakaurawa kana wakafa kana bwiro\x + Eki. 12.22.\x*.
\v 19 Zvino wakachena achasasa pane asina kuchena nezuva retatu nepazuva rechinomwe\x + 19.12.\x*; zvino nezuva rechinomwe achamuchenura\x + Rev. 14.9.\x*; \add iye\add* agosuka nguvo dzake nekuzvishambidza mumvura, agova wakachena madekwani\x + Rev. 15.5.\x*.
\v 20 Asi murume asina kuchena akasazvichenura, mweya uyu uchagurwa kubva pakati peungano, nokuti wasvibisa imba tsvene yaJehovha; mvura yekuparadzanisa haina kusaswa paari; haana kuchena\x + 19.13.\x*.
\v 21 Zvino chichava chimiso nekusingaperi kwavari, kuti anosasa mvura yekuparadzanisa achasuka nguvo dzake; uye anogunzva mvura yekuparadzanisa achava asina kuchena kusvika madekwani.
\v 22 Nechipi nechipi asina kuchena chaanogunzva chichava chisina kuchena; uye mweya uno\add chi\add*gunzva uchava usina kuchena kusvika madekwani\x + Hag. 2.13.\x*.